(454, '1', 'sc_admin/product/create', 'POST', '::1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/108.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '{\"kind\":\"0\",\"descriptions\":{\"en\":{\"name\":\"Laptop HP 15s-fq5079TU (i5-1235U\\/RAM 8GB\\/512GB SSD\\/ Windows 11)\",\"keyword\":\"Laptop HP\",\"description\":\"CPU: Intel Core i5-1235U\",\"content\":\"<h2><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/phongvu.vn\\/c\\/laptop\\\">Laptop<\\/a>&nbsp;HP 15s-fq5079TU 6K799PA l&agrave; d&ograve;ng laptop cao c\\u1ea5p \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf v\\u1edbi ki\\u1ec3u d&aacute;ng thanh l\\u1ecbch, tinh t\\u1ebf h\\u01b0\\u1edbng t\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng h\\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi&ecirc;n v&agrave; v\\u0103n ph&ograve;ng. HP 15s s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu c\\u1ea5u h&igrave;nh m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd v\\u1edbi CPU Intel Core i5-1235U \\u0111em \\u0111\\u1ebfn nhi\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111&aacute;p \\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhu c\\u1ea7u h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp v&agrave; l&agrave;m vi\\u1ec7c c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n m\\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch tho\\u1ea3i m&aacute;i.<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure><img alt=\\\"Laptop HP 15s-fq5079TU 6K799PA \\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/storage.googleapis.com\\/teko-gae.appspot.com\\/media\\/image\\/2022\\/9\\/28\\/20220928_969f26ff-1300-408f-9765-97e2fbff0318.png\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Ngo\\u1ea1i h&igrave;nh m&agrave;u b\\u1ea1c \\u0111\\u1eb3ng c\\u1ea5p, t\\u1ed5ng th\\u1ec3 sang tr\\u1ecdng<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Laptop HP 15s&nbsp;<\\/strong>\\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf v\\u1edbi t\\u1ed5ng th\\u1ec3 sang tr\\u1ecdng v\\u1edbi to&agrave;n b\\u1ed9 m&aacute;y \\u0111\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u1ee7 m\\u1ed9t&nbsp;<strong>m&agrave;u b\\u1ea1c&nbsp;<\\/strong>\\u0111\\u1eb9p m\\u1eaft c&ugrave;ng v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c vi\\u1ec1n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c g\\u1ecdt m\\u1ecfng v&agrave; bo tr&ograve;n t\\u1ec9 m\\u1ec9, tinh