(736, '1', 'sc_admin/product/create', 'POST', '::1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/108.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '{\"kind\":\"0\",\"descriptions\":{\"en\":{\"name\":\"M\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh LCD MSI Optix G27C7 (1920 x 1080\\/VA\\/165Hz\\/1 ms\\/FreeSync Premium)\",\"keyword\":\"M\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh LCD MSI\",\"description\":\"K\\u00edch th\\u01b0\\u1edbc: 27\\\" (1920 x 1080), T\\u1ef7 l\\u1ec7 16:9\",\"content\":\"<h2><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/phongvu.vn\\/man-hinh-may-tinh-scat.03-N001\\\">M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh<\\/a>&nbsp;LCD MSI 27&#39;&#39; Optix G27C7 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb b\\u1ea3ng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u khi\\u1ec3n th\\u1eddi gian ph\\u1ea3n h\\u1ed3i \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng, h\\u1ee9a h\\u1eb9n s\\u1ebd mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn cho b\\u1ea1n nh\\u1eefng l\\u1ee3i th\\u1ebf c\\u1ea1nh tranh c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ec3 h\\u1ea1 g\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u1ed1i th\\u1ee7. V\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u t&iacute;nh n\\u0103ng v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t tr\\u1ed9i, m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cao c\\u1ea5p c\\u1ee7a MSI cho ph&eacute;p b\\u1ea1n tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m ch\\u01a1i game c\\u1ef1c k\\u1ef3 m\\u01b0\\u1ee3t m&agrave;.&nbsp;<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><strong>Thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd, t\\u1ea5m n\\u1ec1n cong \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng<\\/strong><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh Optix G27C7 s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf t\\u1ed1i gi\\u1ea3n v\\u1edbi ch&acirc;n \\u0111\\u1ebf ch\\u1eef V thanh m\\u1ea3nh, v\\u1eeba gi&uacute;p n&acirc;ng \\u0111\\u1ee1 ph\\u1ea7n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh v\\u1eeba t\\u1ea1o n&ecirc;n t\\u1ed5ng th\\u1ec3 sang tr\\u1ecdng. M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh v\\u1edbi vi\\u1ec1n si&ecirc;u h\\u1eb9p, cho ph&eacute;p c&aacute;c game th\\u1ee7 t\\u1eadn h\\u01b0\\u1edfng c\\u1ea3m gi&aacute;c \\u0111\\u1eafm ch&igrave;m t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 trong c&aacute;c tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i v\\u1edbi thi\\u1ebft l\\u1eadp \\u0111a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh 180 \\u0111\\u1ed9, tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m s\\u1ef1 li\\u1ec1n m\\u1ea1ch \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng gi\\u1eefa c&aacute;c m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh khi ch\\u01a1i tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure><img alt=\\\"M\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh LCD MSI 27\'\' Optix G27C7 (1920 x 1080, VA, 165Hz, 1ms, Freesync Premium) | Thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/storage.googleapis.com\\/teko-gae.appspot.com\\/media\\/image\\/2022\\/7\\/1\\/20220701_aef1722c-6659-46e2-b88e-0bf91ef082d8.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh MSI Curved Gaming hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang b\\u1ecb t\\u1ea5m n\\u1ec1n hi\\u1ec3n th\\u1ecb cong c&oacute; t\\u1ef7 l\\u1ec7 cong 1500R, mang \\u0111\\u1ebfn s\\u1ef1 tho\\u1ea3i m&aacute;i v&agrave; ph&ugrave; h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng t\\u1eeb m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh \\u0111\\u1ebfn ch\\u01a1i game. T\\u1ea5m n\\u1ec1n cong c\\u0169ng cho ph&eacute;p b\\u1ea1n c&oacute; c\\u1ea3m gi&aacute;c s\\u1ed1ng \\u0111\\u1ed9ng nh\\u01b0 th\\u1eadt trong tr&ograve; ch\\u01a1i, gi&uacute;p b\\u1ea1n k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u h\\u01a1n v\\u1edbi tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m tr\\u1ecdn v\\u1eb9n, kh&ocirc;ng b\\u1ecb gi\\u1edbi h\\u1ea1n b\\u1edfi kh&ocirc;ng gian hi\\u1ec3n th\\u1ecb.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<figure><img alt=\\\"M\\u00e0n h\\u00ecnh LCD MSI 27\'\' Optix G27C7 (1920 x 1080, VA, 165Hz, 1ms, Freesync Premium) | T\\u1ea5m n\\u1ec1n cong \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/storage.googleapis.com\\/teko-gae.appspot.com\\/media\\/image\\/2022\\/7\\/1\\/20220701_b055be40-abbd-4f4a-81dd-f50ac0b25a83.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/figure>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h4><strong>Tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed9ng si&ecirc;u m\\u01b0\\u1ee3t, h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 g&oacute;c nh&igrave;n r\\u1ed9ng<\\/strong><\\/h4>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh Optix t&iacute;ch h\\u1ee3p b