('97f20840-1b02-4220-9581-f07bde8fcfc5', 'vi', '8 l do m bn nn b ti ngay chic ng h Garmin thng minh', '8 l do m bn nn b ti ngay chic ng h Garmin thng minh', 'Nhc n nhng thng hiu ng h thng minh, khng th khng k n thng hiu ng h Garmin v cng ni ting.', '<h2>1. &aacute;nh gi&aacute; v thng hiu ng h th&ocirc;ng minh Garmin</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi nhc n thng hiu ng h Garmin, ngi ta s nh n nhng mu ng h vi thit k tr trung, nng ng mang hi hng th thao nhng cng kh&ocirc;ng k&eacute;m phn thanh lch. Tr th&agrave;nh thng hiu ng h c&oacute; ch ng tr&ecirc;n th trng, ng h Garmin &atilde; chinh phc kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng bng s uy t&iacute;n v&agrave; cht lng sn phm.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure>\r\n<figure><img alt=\"ng h garmin\" data-id=\"74079\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"450\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-2.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-2.png 800w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-2-300x169.png 300w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-2-768x432.png 768w\" title=\"8 l do m bn nn b ti ngay chic ng h Garminthng minh 1\" width=\"800\" />\r\n<figcaption>ng h Garmin &atilde; chinh phc kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng bng s uy t&iacute;n v&agrave; cht lng sn phm.&nbsp;</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<p>ng h Garmin ra i v&agrave;o nm 1989 vi tr s c t ti M. Sau n&agrave;y, thng hiu c&oacute; thc hin mt s s&aacute;p nhp vi mt thng hiu n t Thy S nhng chung quy Garmin vn l&agrave; thng hiu ng h th&ocirc;ng minh n t M. Nh nhiu thng hiu n t Ch&acirc;u &Acirc;u, Garmin c&oacute; c&aacute;c nh&agrave; m&aacute;y sn xut ng h tr&ecirc;n khp th gii. V&igrave; vy, i k&egrave;m vi thng hiu ng h th&ocirc;ng minh Garmin s c&oacute; gn th&ecirc;m d&ograve;ng &ldquo;Made in&hellip;&rdquo;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thng hiu ng h th&ocirc;ng minh Garmin &atilde; c&oacute; mt kh&aacute; l&acirc;u tr&ecirc;n th trng. X&acirc;y dng h&igrave;nh nh vi sn phm cht lng, uy t&iacute;n v&agrave; gi&aacute; c cnh tranh. Thng hiu ng h Garmin &atilde; v&agrave; ang tr th&agrave;nh mt trong nhng thng hiu &aacute;ng gi&aacute; vi nhng s thay i, ci tin ph&ugrave; hp vi xu th chung ca th gii. H&atilde;y c&ugrave;ng Phong V im qua nhng t&iacute;nh nng v&agrave; c im ni bt ca thng hiu ng h Garmin nh&eacute;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>2. u &atilde;i ln t Phong V d&agrave;nh cho Garmin</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Garmin s l&agrave; ngi bn ng h&agrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng th thiu trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh theo d&otilde;i v&agrave; chm s&oacute;c sc khe ca bn. S hu ngay&nbsp;<a href=\"https://phongvu.vn/c/dong-ho-garmin?utm_source=social&amp;utm_medium=technews&amp;utm_campaign=dong-ho-garmin\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">ng h Garmin ti Phong V gim n 15%</a>. c bit tng k&egrave;m balo Garmin m&agrave;u en th thao nng ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>ng qu&ecirc;n nhp m&atilde; PV100 gim th&ecirc;m 100K khi thanh to&aacute;n VNPAY-QR bn nh&eacute;!</p>\r\n\r\n<figure>\r\n<figure><img alt=\"dong ho garmin 5\" data-id=\"74084\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"450\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-5.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-5.png 800w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-5-300x169.png 300w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-5-768x432.png 768w\" title=\"8 l do m bn nn b ti ngay chic ng h Garminthng minh 2\" width=\"800\" />\r\n<figcaption>ng h Garmin ang c sale 15% ti ca h&agrave;ng Phong V.</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<p>C&oacute; th n&oacute;i, ng h Garmin rt ph&ugrave; hp vi d&acirc;n th thao, nhng ngi u ti&ecirc;n s nng ng, mnh m  hot ng li&ecirc;n tc trong thi gian d&agrave;i. B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, nu bit c&aacute;ch t&igrave;m hiu v&agrave; khai th&aacute;c trit  nhng t&iacute;nh nng c&oacute; tr&ecirc;n ng h Garmin. Bn c&oacute; th bin chic ng h th&ocirc;ng minh ca m&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh mt hun luyn vi&ecirc;n c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c bn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>3. 8 t&iacute;nh nng ni bt ca ng h Garmin</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Thng hiu ng h Garmin lu&ocirc;n mang n cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng nhng sn phm ng h th&ocirc;ng minh th thao vi thit k v&agrave; t&iacute;nh nng v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng n tng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>3.1 V thit k</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>a phn c&aacute;c mu ng h Garmin l&agrave; d&ograve;ng sn phm th thao vi thit k tr trung, nng ng. Mt ng h th&ocirc;ng minh Garmin l&agrave; dng mt tr&ograve;n d nh&igrave;n, d s dng, ph&ugrave; hp vi nhiu i tng kh&aacute;c nhau. Tuy thit k ca ng h Garmin tr&ocirc;ng kh&aacute; hm h v&agrave; th thao nhng n&oacute; vn m bo c n&eacute;t thanh lch vn c&oacute; ca mt chic ng h mt tr&ograve;n n&ecirc;n vn ph&ugrave; hp vi n gii.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure>\r\n<figure><img alt=\"dong ho garmin 1\" data-id=\"74080\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"450\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-1.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-1.png 800w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-1-300x169.png 300w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-1-768x432.png 768w\" title=\"8 l do m bn nn b ti ngay chic ng h Garminthng minh 3\" width=\"800\" />\r\n<figcaption>ng h Garmin l&agrave; d&ograve;ng sn phm th thao vi thit k tr trung, nng ng.</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<p>ng h Garmin thng s dng c&aacute;c vt liu cao cp cho c&aacute;c mu ng h  d&agrave;nh ri&ecirc;ng cho c&aacute;c hot ng th thao mnh ngo&agrave;i tri. Nhng vt liu c&oacute; th k n nh l&agrave; th&eacute;p, nha gia cng, k&iacute;nh cng lc, k&iacute;nh sapphire, lp m DLC&hellip; Vic s dng cht liu cao cp gi&uacute;p ng h Garmin lu&ocirc;n bn b trong iu kin hot ng mnh v&agrave; li&ecirc;n tc. D&acirc;y eo ng h c l&agrave;m t silicon vi nhiu phi&ecirc;n bn m&agrave;u sc n&ecirc;n ng h Garmin rt bn b v&agrave; v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng thi thng.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mc  ho&agrave;n thin sn phm ca ng h Garmin lu&ocirc;n  mc rt cao, hu nh kh&ocirc;ng th t&igrave;m thy c&aacute;c chi tit nha tha ra tr&ecirc;n phn th&acirc;n v, d&acirc;y hay n&uacute;t bm. iu n&agrave;y to n&ecirc;n uy t&iacute;n v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng r&otilde; r&agrave;ng cho thng hiu ng h th&ocirc;ng minh n&agrave;y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>3.2 V m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>ng h Garmin c ho&agrave;n thin vi m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh Memory In Pixel (MIP) cho kh nng nh&igrave;n ngo&agrave;i tri tt v&agrave; cht lng h&igrave;nh nh rt r&otilde; n&eacute;t. Nhng hot ng ngo&agrave;i tri lu&ocirc;n c ti u mang li s h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh s dng sn phm ca kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&ocirc;ng ngh MIP c&oacute; hai u im ni bt nh sau: Mt l&agrave; gi&uacute;p tit kim pin, tng thi gian s dng. Hai l&agrave; hin th r&otilde; n&eacute;t d&ugrave; cho  ngo&agrave;i tri nng gt hay l&agrave;  trong nh&agrave;. Nh u im ni bt n&agrave;y m&agrave; ng h Garmin c&oacute; th c s dng vi mc  hin th th&ocirc;ng tin cao nhng li rt tit kim pin. C th, bn c&oacute; th ng dng n&oacute; trong t&iacute;nh nng dn ng vi nhng ngi a th&iacute;ch th thao v&agrave; mo him khi phi i trong nhng con ng kh&ocirc;ng quen thuc.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure>\r\n<figure><img alt=\"dong ho garmin 6\" data-id=\"74081\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"450\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-6.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-6.png 800w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-6-300x169.png 300w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-6-768x432.png 768w\" title=\"8 l do m bn nn b ti ngay chic ng h Garminthng minh 4\" width=\"800\" />\r\n<figcaption>ng h Garmin c&oacute; th c s dng vi mc  hin th th&ocirc;ng tin cao nhng li rt tit kim pin.</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh ca ng h Garmin li c&oacute; kh&aacute; &iacute;t m&agrave;u sc v&agrave;  ph&acirc;n gii ch  mc trung b&igrave;nh. iu n&agrave;y s kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; nh hng n bn trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh s dng v&igrave; ng h Garmin c ti u h&oacute;a mi th  n&acirc;ng cao thi lng s dng vi nhng hot ng th thao.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>3.3 C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng GPS chuy&ecirc;n dng</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Bng kinh nghim ch to c&aacute;c thit b dn ng bng GPS, Garmin &atilde; &aacute;p dng v&agrave; bin chic ng h th&ocirc;ng minh ca h th&agrave;nh mt thit b dn ng v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng hiu qu vi c&aacute;c ch  dn ng kh&aacute;c nhau:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Real-time turn-by-turn navigation: Dn ng theo thi gian thc bng GPS.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Trendline Popularity Routing: Thng k&ecirc; c&aacute;c ng chy ph bin trong khu vc xung quanh.</li>\r\n	<li>Round-trip Routing: To ng chy v&ograve;ng kh&eacute;p k&iacute;n theo c ly v&agrave; hng xut ph&aacute;t c ngi d&ugrave;ng nh sn.</li>\r\n	<li>Points of Interst and Trail Data: D liu bn  chy trail chi tit.</li>\r\n	<li>ClimbPro Ascent Feature: Ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch chi tit d liu v c&aacute;c on dc m&agrave; ngi d&ugrave;ng cn phi leo/chy.</li>\r\n	<li>PacePro Feature: L&ecirc;n k hoch v&agrave; nhc nh ngi d&ugrave;ng ph&acirc;n phi sc lc trong ng chy.</li>\r\n	<li>Tracback: o ngc on ng &atilde; i  dn ngi d&ugrave;ng quay li ni bt u i lc (hoc ni xut ph&aacute;t).</li>\r\n	<li>Sight&rsquo;N Go: Kho&aacute; nh hng bng vt th  dn ng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>3.4 C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng theo d&otilde;i sc khe</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.garmin.com/vi-VN/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Garmin</a>&nbsp;l&agrave; mt trong nhng i t&aacute;c ca Fristbeat &ndash; c&ocirc;ng ty chuy&ecirc;n cung cp v&agrave; ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch c&aacute;c sn phm o c v th&ocirc;ng s sc khe, th trng vn ng. V&igrave; vy, c&aacute;c thit b ca Garmin lu&ocirc;n c cp nht v&agrave; trang b nhng sn phm mi nht n t Firstbeat. iu n&agrave;y to n&ecirc;n sc cnh tranh rt ln ca Garmin vi nhng thng hiu kh&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n th trng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure>\r\n<figure><img alt=\"dong ho garmin 4\" data-id=\"74082\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"450\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-4.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-4.png 800w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-4-300x169.png 300w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-4-768x432.png 768w\" title=\"8 l do m bn nn b ti ngay chic ng h Garminthng minh 5\" width=\"800\" />\r\n<figcaption>ng h Garmin lu&ocirc;n c cp nht v&agrave; trang b nhng sn phm mi nht n t Firstbeat.</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<h3>3.5 Kh nng ng b vi thit b di ng</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Chc hn &acirc;y l&agrave; iu m&agrave; mi ngi rt quan t&acirc;m v&igrave; ng h th&ocirc;ng minh phi c kt ni vi di ng th&igrave; mi hin th nhng th&ocirc;ng tin cng nh l&agrave; d liu cn thit. ng h Garmin l&agrave;m rt tt vic n&agrave;y. Bn c&oacute; th kt ni vi thit b di ng, nhn th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o, cuc gi, tin nhn, iu chnh nhc m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn phi m in thoi. Ngo&agrave;i ra, bn c&ograve;n c&oacute; th iu chnh giao din ng h theo s th&iacute;ch ca c&aacute; nh&acirc;n m&igrave;nh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>3.6 Thi lng pin</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>V khong thi lng pin s dng, ng h Garmin lu&ocirc;n l&agrave;m tt khi m bo sn phm ca m&igrave;nh lu&ocirc;n t c mc s dng v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng &ldquo;tr&acirc;u&rdquo; l&ecirc;n n 7 ng&agrave;y hoc 15 ng&agrave;y m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn sc. Vi ch  GPS th&igrave; bn c&oacute; th s dng l&ecirc;n n 13 ng&agrave;y cho mt chic ng h th&ocirc;ng minh Garmin. &acirc;y l&agrave; mt im cng v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng t gi&aacute; cho d&acirc;n chi c&ocirc;ng ngh v&igrave; bn s kh&ocirc;ng cn phi lo lng lu&ocirc;n phi nh sc pin cho ng h trc khi ra ngo&agrave;i.</p>\r\n\r\n<figure>\r\n<figure><img alt=\"dong ho garmin 3\" data-id=\"74083\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"450\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-3.png\" srcset=\"https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-3.png 800w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-3-300x169.png 300w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/dong-ho-garmin-3-768x432.png 768w\" title=\"8 l do m bn nn b ti ngay chic ng h Garminthng minh 6\" width=\"800\" />\r\n<figcaption>ng h Garmin c&oacute; mc pin l&ecirc;n n 7 ng&agrave;y hoc 15 ng&agrave;y m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn sc.</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<h3>3.7  bn</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>L&agrave; d&ograve;ng sn phm ng h th&ocirc;ng minh phc v cho th thao n&ecirc;n v  bn v&agrave; gia c&ocirc;ng, ng h Garmin lu&ocirc;n l&agrave;m rt tt. Bn c&oacute; th thoi m&aacute;i s dng chic ng h n&agrave;y khi bi li, chy b, leo n&uacute;i, p xe&hellip; ng h Garmin cho cht lng chng va p, chng nc, chng try xc rt cao. V&igrave; vy, bn ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c&oacute; th y&ecirc;n t&acirc;m s dng ng h Garmin trong thi gian d&agrave;i m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn phi lo hng h&oacute;c.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>3.8 Gi&aacute; th&agrave;nh</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>L&agrave; d&ograve;