atilde; h&oacute;a u cui tin nhn Zalo</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3> n&acirc;ng cp M&atilde; h&oacute;a u cui tr&ecirc;n in thoi:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Bc 1: Chn cuc tr&ograve; chuyn m&agrave; bn mun m&atilde; h&oacute;a, v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong>T&ugrave;y chn</strong>, n chn&nbsp;<strong>M&atilde; h&oacute;a u cui</strong>&nbsp;v&agrave; chn&nbsp;<strong>N&acirc;ng cp</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bc 2: i qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh n&acirc;ng cp ho&agrave;n tt l&agrave; bn &atilde; c&oacute; th gi tin nhn m&atilde; h&oacute;a cho i phng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3> n&acirc;ng cp M&atilde; h&oacute;a u cui tr&ecirc;n Zalo PC:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Bc 1: Trong tr&ograve; chuyn cn n&acirc;ng cp, v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong>Th&ocirc;ng tin hi thoi</strong>, tip tc K&eacute;o xung v&agrave; n v&agrave;o phn&nbsp;<strong>Thit lp bo mt</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bc 2: Ti phn Thit lp bo mt, bm v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong>M&atilde; h&oacute;a u cui&nbsp;</strong>&gt;&nbsp;<strong>N&acirc;ng cp m&atilde; h&oacute;a u cui</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bc 3: Ch qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh n&acirc;ng cp ho&agrave;n tt</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh n&acirc;ng cp ho&agrave;n tt, b&ecirc;n cnh cuc tr&ograve; chuyn s hin th biu tng  kh&oacute;a  bn d d&agrave;ng ph&acirc;n bit vi nhng t&agrave;i khon cha c cp nht t&iacute;nh nng n&agrave;y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"tin-nhan-ma-hoa-dau-cuoi-zalo\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"490\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/tin-nhan-ma-hoa-dau-cuoi-zalo.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/tin-nhan-ma-hoa-dau-cuoi-zalo.jpg 800w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/tin-nhan-ma-hoa-dau-cuoi-zalo-300x184.jpg 300w, https://cdn.image.phongvu.vn/cong-nghe/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/tin-nhan-ma-hoa-dau-cuoi-zalo-768x470.jpg 768w\" title=\"Cch bt v tt tnh nng tin nhn m ha u cui Zalo 4\" width=\"800\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<h3>4.2 Tt m&atilde; h&oacute;a tin nhn u cui Zalo</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin nay Zalo cha cho ph&eacute;p ngi d&ugrave;ng tt i t&iacute;nh nng m&atilde; h&oacute;a tin nhn u cui khi &atilde; m t&iacute;nh nng n&agrave;y l&ecirc;n. Bn cng n&ecirc;n c&acirc;n nhc tht k trc khi tin h&agrave;nh n&acirc;ng cp tin nhn nh&eacute;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh&agrave; ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh Zalo cng cha cho bit thi im m&agrave; t&iacute;nh nng m&atilde; h&oacute;a tin nhn u cui c ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh phi&ecirc;n bn ch&iacute;nh thc n&ecirc;n hi vng trong tng lai ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; th tt c t&iacute;nh nng n&agrave;y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>5. Mt s li thng gp phi khi n&acirc;ng cp tin nhn m&atilde; h&oacute;a u cui Zalo</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh tri nghim hn 1 tun ca t&iacute;nh nng n&agrave;y, m&igrave;nh nhn thy mt s li m&agrave; Zalo cn khc phc nh:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Li gii m&atilde; tin nhn kh&ocirc;ng th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng: Vi nhng ngi d&ugrave;ng va s dng PC v&agrave; smartphone th&igrave; rt thng hay gp vn  li tin nhn m&atilde; gii m&atilde; kh&ocirc;ng th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng. Bn kh&ocirc;ng th khc phc c t&igrave;nh trng n&agrave;y v&agrave; ch c&oacute; mt c&aacute;ch duy nht l&agrave; nh ngi gi gi li tin nhn nu mun xem  mt thit b kh&aacute;c.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Kh&ocirc;ng t&igrave;m li c tin nhn ngay c tr&ecirc;n in thoi v&agrave; PC. &acirc;y l&agrave; mt li kh&aacute; nghi&ecirc;m trng v&igrave; vi nhng ngi d&ugrave;ng thng xuy&ecirc;n sao lu d liu ni dung tin nhn tr&ecirc;n ng dng th&igrave; li n&agrave;y khin ngi d&ugrave;ng t&igrave;m li tin nhn kh&oacute; khn hn.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Vi nhng t&agrave;i khon &atilde; n&acirc;ng cp l&ecirc;n chun tin nhn m&atilde; h&oacute;a u cui th&igrave; ngi d&ugrave;ng cng kh&ocirc;ng th gi nh trc tip t album na. iu n&agrave;y s rt mt thi gian  bn t&igrave;m li h&igrave;nh nh mun gi trong mc tin nhn.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>');
