=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"line-height:1.8em\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\">Tr&ecirc;n &acirc;y l&agrave; b&agrave;i vit Phong V chia s c&aacute;ch xem t s c&aacute;c cp trn World Cup 2022 bng t&iacute;nh nng Live Activities. T&iacute;nh nng n&agrave;y s gi&uacute;p ngi d&ugrave;ng thun tin hn khi theo d&otilde;i t s c&aacute;c trn u World Cup 2022. Hy vng qua b&agrave;i vit n&agrave;y, bn &atilde; bit c c&aacute;ch  s dng t&iacute;nh nng Live Activities tr&ecirc;n iPhone phi&ecirc;n bn iOS 16  theo d&otilde;i c&aacute;c trn u World Cup 2022. Ch&uacute;c c&aacute;c bn c&oacute; mt m&ugrave;a World Cup 2022 tht &aacute;ng nh vi c&aacute;c trn cu nh cao.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"background:#ffffff\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"outline:0px\"><span style=\"vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word\"><span style=\"line-height:1.8em\"><span style=\"color:#444444\"><span style=\"font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"> c&oacute; tri nghim cht lng hn trong m&ugrave;a World Cup 2022 n&agrave;y. H&atilde;y n c&aacute;c ca h&agrave;ng ca Phong V tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n quc  sm ngay cho m&igrave;nh nhng chic in thoi vi m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh ln, &acirc;m thanh cht lng  tn hng nhng trn cu nh cao ngay nh&eacute;!</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;'),
('97f209f2-a26d-404d-ac5c-29dc48a14b0e', 'en', 'Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l', 'Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l', 'Theo dng s kin Android 13  c Google cng b chnh thc gn y th u thng 10 ny, hng in thoi nh m Samsung cng cho ra mt phin bn h iu hnh in thoi th h mi c tn Samsung One UI 5.0', '<h2>1. Nhng t&iacute;nh nng mi m tr&ecirc;n One UI 5.0&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. 1 M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh kh&oacute;a th&ocirc;ng minh hn tr&ecirc;n One UI 5.0</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mt trong nhng n&acirc;ng cp &aacute;ng gi&aacute; v&agrave; cng c Samsung chm ch&uacute;t nhiu nht tr&ecirc;n phi&ecirc;n bn h iu h&agrave;nh mi &oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh kh&oacute;a.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H&atilde;ng &atilde; em n cho ngi d&ugrave;ng rt nhiu kiu t&ugrave;y bin th&uacute; v  bn c&oacute; th c&aacute; nh&acirc;n h&oacute;a chic in thoi ca m&igrave;nh. Kh&ocirc;ng ch s hu nhiu h&igrave;nh nn c &aacute;o, One UI 5 c&ograve;n cho ph&eacute;p ngi d&ugrave;ng thay i nhiu kiu mt ng h hin th kh&aacute;c nhau t ng h kim n ng h s in t.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, bn cng c&oacute; th iu chnh k&iacute;ch thc hin th ca ng h cng nh h&igrave;nh thc hin th ca c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh kh&oacute;a, thay i font ch, kiu ch, kiu hin th th&ocirc;ng tin dng ch hoc icon.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V h&igrave;nh nn th&igrave; ngi d&ugrave;ng s c la chn rt nhiu h&igrave;nh nn mc nh ca h thng, h&igrave;nh nn theo m&agrave;u sc v&agrave; c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh nn c kt ni th&ocirc;ng qua ng dng Galaxy Store. Ngo&agrave;i ra, bn cng c&oacute; th to mt video l&agrave;m h&igrave;nh nn thay v&igrave; mt nh tnh nh trc &acirc;y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tht ra nhng c&agrave;i t n&agrave;y &atilde; c Samsung t&iacute;ch hp trong ng dng Good Lock trc &acirc;y nhng vi phi&ecirc;n bn n&agrave;y th&igrave; bn &atilde; c&oacute; th s dng trc tip tr&ecirc;n h thng m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn c&agrave;i t ng dng n&agrave;y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh&igrave;n chung, m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh kh&oacute;a mi ca One UI 5.0 &atilde; em li tri nghim th&uacute; v hn nhiu so vi trc. Bn c&oacute; th c&agrave;i t nhanh h&igrave;nh nn bng c&aacute;ch n gi v&agrave;o m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn v&agrave;o C&agrave;i t nh trc &acirc;y. Nu so s&aacute;nh vi h iu h&agrave;nh iOS 16 tr&ecirc;n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://phongvu.vn/c/iphone\">iPhone</a>&nbsp;th&igrave; h iu h&agrave;nh ca Samsung kh&ocirc;ng h k&eacute;m cnh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1.2. Material You m&agrave;u sc hn</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Giao din m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh ch&iacute;nh tr&ecirc;n One UI 5 c b sung th&ecirc;m nhiu t&iacute;nh nng th&ocirc;ng minh nh Smart Suggestions &ndash; t ng gi &yacute; nhng ng dng thng xuy&ecirc;n c s dng hoc nhng ng dng m&agrave; h thng ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch l&agrave; bn s cn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, t&iacute;nh nng Stack Widgets cng c b sung  bn c&oacute; th th&ecirc;m nhiu widget kh&aacute;c nhau v&agrave;o c&ugrave;ng mt khung duy nht  tit kim c kh&ocirc;ng gian hin th. Tr&ecirc;n h iu h&agrave;nh tin nhim&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.samsung.com/vn/support/mobile-devices/what-are-the-new-features-and-upgrades-of-one-ui-4-1/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">One UI 4.1</a>&nbsp;th&igrave; mi mt widget s c hin th  mt khung kh&aacute;c nhau chim nhiu din t&iacute;ch m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"giao-dien-samsung-one-ui-5-0\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/PTFCbbzt-giao-dien-samsung-one-ui-5-0.jpg\" title=\"Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l 1\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>H thng icon, m&agrave;u sc tr&ecirc;n One UI 5 c Samsung ng b theo h thng  to n&ecirc;n s h&agrave;i h&ograve;a tr&ecirc;n thit b. Color Palette tr&ecirc;n One UI 5.0 cng c b sung th&ecirc;m nhiu bng phi m&agrave;u l&ecirc;n n 12 bng m&agrave;u, nhiu hn 4 bng m&agrave;u tr&ecirc;n h iu h&agrave;nh c.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. 3. Modes &amp; Routines</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>T&iacute;nh nng Modes &amp; Routines tr&ecirc;n iOS tng khin nhiu SamFan ao c nay &atilde; c Samsung t&iacute;ch hp v&agrave;o h iu h&agrave;nh One UI 5.0. T&iacute;nh nng n&agrave;y s cho ph&eacute;p bn thit lp c&aacute;c ng cnh mc nh tr&ecirc;n h thng nh Sleep, Driving, Exercise, Relax, Work v&agrave; bn cng c&oacute; th to th&ecirc;m nhiu ng cnh kh&aacute;c theo &yacute; mun.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi m t&iacute;nh nng Modes &amp; Routines th&igrave; in thoi s t ng tt i nhng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o trng th&aacute;i kh&ocirc;ng cn thit v&agrave; ch cho ph&eacute;p nhng h&agrave;nh ng nht nh din ra tr&ecirc;n in thoi, t &oacute; gi&uacute;p bn tp trung hn cho c&ocirc;ng vic hay hot ng ca m&igrave;nh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"mode-samsung-one-ui-5-0\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/HdduI6YX-mode-samsung-one-ui-5-0.jpg\" title=\"Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l 2\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. 4. a nhim nhiu ca s th&acirc;n thin hn&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Trc &acirc;y, khi mun a nhim nhiu ca s tr&ecirc;n in thoi th&igrave; thit b ca bn phi c h tr Samsung DeX. iu n&agrave;y s kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n cn thit khi in thoi ca bn c n&acirc;ng cp l&ecirc;n h iu h&agrave;nh One UI 5.0, t&iacute;nh nng a nhim nhiu ca s s c c&agrave;i t mc nh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p> thit lp c&agrave;i t n&agrave;y, bn c&oacute; th thc hin bng c&aacute;ch&nbsp;<strong>Settings -&gt; Advanced Features -&gt; Labs -&gt; Multi Window for all apps.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>L&uacute;c n&agrave;y, bn c&oacute; th s dng c ch vut t g&oacute;c m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh xung  thu nh ca s ang s dng, tip theo bn c&oacute; th m mt ng dng kh&aacute;c v&agrave; s dng song song hai ca s n&agrave;y mt c&aacute;ch b&igrave;nh thng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"One-UI-5\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/eiC5Pnc3-One-UI-5.jpg\" title=\"Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l 3\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>One IU 5 cho ph&eacute;p bn m v&agrave; m nhim l&ecirc;n n 5 ca s hoc ng dng c&ugrave;ng l&uacute;c, tuy nhi&ecirc;n t&iacute;nh nng n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng em li qu&aacute; nhiu li &iacute;ch cho ngi d&ugrave;ng v&igrave; din t&iacute;ch hin th ca m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh in thoi kh&aacute; nh  bn c&oacute; th theo d&otilde;i ht c tt c c&aacute;c ni dung.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, khi mun chia &ocirc;i m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh vi 2 ca s kh&aacute;c nhau th&igrave; bn c&oacute; th vut 2 ng&oacute;n tay t cnh di m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh l&ecirc;n  m Split View. Thanh iu khin t&aacute;c v v&agrave; status bar l&uacute;c n&agrave;y s c n  tn dng to&agrave;n b kh&ocirc;ng gian hin th ca m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. 5. C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng kh&aacute; th&uacute; v vi Camera ca m&aacute;y</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung cng &atilde; em n mt s chc nng kh&aacute; c &aacute;o cho ngi d&ugrave;ng khi s dng camera tr&ecirc;n in thoi &atilde; c l&ecirc;n h iu h&agrave;nh One UI 5.0. C th,  ch  chp  n c t&iacute;ch hp k&egrave;m vi phn c&agrave;i t camera th&igrave; bn c&oacute; th&ecirc;m kh nng zoom 3x. Bn cng c&oacute; th th&ecirc;m trc tip Watermark v&agrave;o nh sau khi chp.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, One UI 5 c&ograve;n em li kh nng nhn din vn bn qua h&igrave;nh nh, bn c&oacute; th chn v&agrave;o khu vc nh c&oacute; cha k&iacute; t  m&aacute;y t ng copy on vn bn &oacute; hoc t&igrave;m kim th&ocirc;ng tin tr&ecirc;n Google.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. 6. Trng th&aacute;i th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o (App Notifications) &amp; c&agrave;i t ng&ocirc;n ng ng dng (App Languages)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i t&ugrave;y chnh h thng giao din, Samsung c&ograve;n mang li cho ngi d&ugrave;ng nhng thit lp m&agrave; bn c&oacute; th thay i khi s dng ng dng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>u ti&ecirc;n, vi t&iacute;nh nng App Notifications th&igrave; bn c&oacute; th tin h&agrave;nh t&ugrave;y chnh c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh thc hin th th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o ca ng dng. C th, Samsung cho bn 3 t&ugrave;y chn mc nh bao gm hin th th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o theo dng banner  lockscreen, hin th s lng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o mi ti icon ng dng v&agrave; hin th ca s pop-up th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o &oacute;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"thong-bao-samsung-one-ui-5-0\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/0WitYJeI-thong-bao-samsung-one-ui-5-0.jpg\" title=\"Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l 4\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, vi tng ng dng c c&agrave;i t trong m&aacute;y, bn cng c&oacute; th t&ugrave;y chnh ng&ocirc;n ng hin th ch&iacute;nh trong ng dng &oacute; nh ting Anh, ting Vit,&hellip;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. 7. Bo mt hn vi Security &amp; Privacy</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Vi h iu h&agrave;nh One IU 4.1 trc &acirc;y th&igrave; bn s nhn thy rt nhiu mc li&ecirc;n quan n bo mt ca m&aacute;y nh &ldquo;Biometrics and Security&rdquo; v&agrave; &ldquo;Privacy Dashboard&rdquo;. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n One Ui 5.0 th&igrave; tt c nhng t&iacute;nh nng bo mt thit b u &atilde; c Samsung gom v&agrave;o c&ugrave;ng mt mc c&oacute; t&ecirc;n Security &amp; Privacy  ngi d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; th theo d&otilde;i v&agrave; qun l&yacute; thit b trc quan hn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kh&ocirc;ng ch qun l&yacute; c quyn truy cp h thng ca c&aacute;c ng dng, cp ph&eacute;p quyn truy cp v&agrave;o camera, micro,.. ca tng ng dng m&agrave; vic qun l&yacute; file, folder tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y cng din ra d d&agrave;ng hn th&ocirc;ng qua Samsung Pass, Secure Folder, Biometrics, Private Share.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>2. C&oacute; n&ecirc;n cp nht One Ui 5.0 kh&ocirc;ng? Danh s&aacute;ch nhng thit b c cp nht phi&ecirc;n bn h iu h&agrave;nh One UI 5</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Giao din tng th ca h iu h&agrave;nh One UI 5 kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; nhiu thay i qu&aacute; ln so vi h iu h&agrave;nh One UI 4.1 trc &oacute; n&ecirc;n n&oacute; vn mang li mt s quen thuc cho ngi d&ugrave;ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, theo &aacute;nh gi&aacute; ca nhiu chuy&ecirc;n trang c&ocirc;ng ngh v&agrave; phn hi t&iacute;ch cc t ngi d&ugrave;ng th&igrave; h iu h&agrave;nh mi ca Samsung mang li tri nghim tng i mt m&agrave; v&agrave; nhiu t&iacute;nh nng &aacute;ng gi&aacute;.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"samsung-one-ui-5-0\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/H3nJ85Tf-samsung-one-ui-5-0.png\" title=\"Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l 5\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, vi vic cp nht One UI 5&nbsp; th&igrave; v c bn bn cng s nhn c nhng ci tin t h iu h&agrave;nh mi Android 13 qua &oacute; gi&uacute;p ci thin hiu sut tr&ecirc;n in thoi ca bn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Danh s&aacute;ch c&aacute;c thit b c cp nht One UI 5:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin ti th&igrave; c&aacute;c phi&ecirc;n bn Samsung Galaxy S22 series &atilde; c cp nht phi&ecirc;n bn ch&iacute;nh thc ca One UI 5.0. Samsung cng &atilde; c&ocirc;ng b l tr&igrave;nh cp nht h iu h&agrave;nh n&agrave;y cho c&aacute;c thit b ca h v&agrave;o cui nm nay v&agrave; u nm 2023.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo &oacute;, c&aacute;c thit b Samsung Galaxy S20, Z Flip 3, Z Fold 3 tr v sau s c cp nht bn ch&iacute;nh thc One UI 5 v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 11.</p>');
INSERT INTO `sc_shop_news_description` (`news_id`, `lang`, `title`, `keyword`, `description`, `content`) VALUES
('97f209f2-a26d-404d-ac5c-29dc48a14b0e', 'vi', 'Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l', 'Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l', 'Theo dng s kin Android 13  c Google cng b chnh thc gn y th u thng 10 ny, hng in thoi nh m Samsung cng cho ra mt phin bn h iu hnh in thoi th h mi c tn Samsung One UI 5.0', '<h2>1. Nhng t&iacute;nh nng mi m tr&ecirc;n One UI 5.0&nbsp;&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. 1 M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh kh&oacute;a th&ocirc;ng minh hn tr&ecirc;n One UI 5.0</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mt trong nhng n&acirc;ng cp &aacute;ng gi&aacute; v&agrave; cng c Samsung chm ch&uacute;t nhiu nht tr&ecirc;n phi&ecirc;n bn h iu h&agrave;nh mi &oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh kh&oacute;a.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H&atilde;ng &atilde; em n cho ngi d&ugrave;ng rt nhiu kiu t&ugrave;y bin th&uacute; v  bn c&oacute; th c&aacute; nh&acirc;n h&oacute;a chic in thoi ca m&igrave;nh. Kh&ocirc;ng ch s hu nhiu h&igrave;nh nn c &aacute;o, One UI 5 c&ograve;n cho ph&eacute;p ngi d&ugrave;ng thay i nhiu kiu mt ng h hin th kh&aacute;c nhau t ng h kim n ng h s in t.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, bn cng c&oacute; th iu chnh k&iacute;ch thc hin th ca ng h cng nh h&igrave;nh thc hin th ca c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh kh&oacute;a, thay i font ch, kiu ch, kiu hin th th&ocirc;ng tin dng ch hoc icon.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V h&igrave;nh nn th&igrave; ngi d&ugrave;ng s c la chn rt nhiu h&igrave;nh nn mc nh ca h thng, h&igrave;nh nn theo m&agrave;u sc v&agrave; c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh nn c kt ni th&ocirc;ng qua ng dng Galaxy Store. Ngo&agrave;i ra, bn cng c&oacute; th to mt video l&agrave;m h&igrave;nh nn thay v&igrave; mt nh tnh nh trc &acirc;y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tht ra nhng c&agrave;i t n&agrave;y &atilde; c Samsung t&iacute;ch hp trong ng dng Good Lock trc &acirc;y nhng vi phi&ecirc;n bn n&agrave;y th&igrave; bn &atilde; c&oacute; th s dng trc tip tr&ecirc;n h thng m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn c&agrave;i t ng dng n&agrave;y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh&igrave;n chung, m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh kh&oacute;a mi ca One UI 5.0 &atilde; em li tri nghim th&uacute; v hn nhiu so vi trc. Bn c&oacute; th c&agrave;i t nhanh h&igrave;nh nn bng c&aacute;ch n gi v&agrave;o m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cn v&agrave;o C&agrave;i t nh trc &acirc;y. Nu so s&aacute;nh vi h iu h&agrave;nh iOS 16 tr&ecirc;n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://phongvu.vn/c/iphone\">iPhone</a>&nbsp;th&igrave; h iu h&agrave;nh ca Samsung kh&ocirc;ng h k&eacute;m cnh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1.2. Material You m&agrave;u sc hn</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Giao din m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh ch&iacute;nh tr&ecirc;n One UI 5 c b sung th&ecirc;m nhiu t&iacute;nh nng th&ocirc;ng minh nh Smart Suggestions &ndash; t ng gi &yacute; nhng ng dng thng xuy&ecirc;n c s dng hoc nhng ng dng m&agrave; h thng ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch l&agrave; bn s cn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, t&iacute;nh nng Stack Widgets cng c b sung  bn c&oacute; th th&ecirc;m nhiu widget kh&aacute;c nhau v&agrave;o c&ugrave;ng mt khung duy nht  tit kim c kh&ocirc;ng gian hin th. Tr&ecirc;n h iu h&agrave;nh tin nhim&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.samsung.com/vn/support/mobile-devices/what-are-the-new-features-and-upgrades-of-one-ui-4-1/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">One UI 4.1</a>&nbsp;th&igrave; mi mt widget s c hin th  mt khung kh&aacute;c nhau chim nhiu din t&iacute;ch m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"giao-dien-samsung-one-ui-5-0\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/PTFCbbzt-giao-dien-samsung-one-ui-5-0.jpg\" title=\"Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l 1\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>H thng icon, m&agrave;u sc tr&ecirc;n One UI 5 c Samsung ng b theo h thng  to n&ecirc;n s h&agrave;i h&ograve;a tr&ecirc;n thit b. Color Palette tr&ecirc;n One UI 5.0 cng c b sung th&ecirc;m nhiu bng phi m&agrave;u l&ecirc;n n 12 bng m&agrave;u, nhiu hn 4 bng m&agrave;u tr&ecirc;n h iu h&agrave;nh c.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. 3. Modes &amp; Routines</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>T&iacute;nh nng Modes &amp; Routines tr&ecirc;n iOS tng khin nhiu SamFan ao c nay &atilde; c Samsung t&iacute;ch hp v&agrave;o h iu h&agrave;nh One UI 5.0. T&iacute;nh nng n&agrave;y s cho ph&eacute;p bn thit lp c&aacute;c ng cnh mc nh tr&ecirc;n h thng nh Sleep, Driving, Exercise, Relax, Work v&agrave; bn cng c&oacute; th to th&ecirc;m nhiu ng cnh kh&aacute;c theo &yacute; mun.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi m t&iacute;nh nng Modes &amp; Routines th&igrave; in thoi s t ng tt i nhng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o trng th&aacute;i kh&ocirc;ng cn thit v&agrave; ch cho ph&eacute;p nhng h&agrave;nh ng nht nh din ra tr&ecirc;n in thoi, t &oacute; gi&uacute;p bn tp trung hn cho c&ocirc;ng vic hay hot ng ca m&igrave;nh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"mode-samsung-one-ui-5-0\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/HdduI6YX-mode-samsung-one-ui-5-0.jpg\" title=\"Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l 2\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. 4. a nhim nhiu ca s th&acirc;n thin hn&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Trc &acirc;y, khi mun a nhim nhiu ca s tr&ecirc;n in thoi th&igrave; thit b ca bn phi c h tr Samsung DeX. iu n&agrave;y s kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n cn thit khi in thoi ca bn c n&acirc;ng cp l&ecirc;n h iu h&agrave;nh One UI 5.0, t&iacute;nh nng a nhim nhiu ca s s c c&agrave;i t mc nh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p> thit lp c&agrave;i t n&agrave;y, bn c&oacute; th thc hin bng c&aacute;ch&nbsp;<strong>Settings -&gt; Advanced Features -&gt; Labs -&gt; Multi Window for all apps.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>L&uacute;c n&agrave;y, bn c&oacute; th s dng c ch vut t g&oacute;c m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh xung  thu nh ca s ang s dng, tip theo bn c&oacute; th m mt ng dng kh&aacute;c v&agrave; s dng song song hai ca s n&agrave;y mt c&aacute;ch b&igrave;nh thng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"One-UI-5\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/eiC5Pnc3-One-UI-5.jpg\" title=\"Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l 3\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>One IU 5 cho ph&eacute;p bn m v&agrave; m nhim l&ecirc;n n 5 ca s hoc ng dng c&ugrave;ng l&uacute;c, tuy nhi&ecirc;n t&iacute;nh nng n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng em li qu&aacute; nhiu li &iacute;ch cho ngi d&ugrave;ng v&igrave; din t&iacute;ch hin th ca m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh in thoi kh&aacute; nh  bn c&oacute; th theo d&otilde;i ht c tt c c&aacute;c ni dung.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, khi mun chia &ocirc;i m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh vi 2 ca s kh&aacute;c nhau th&igrave; bn c&oacute; th vut 2 ng&oacute;n tay t cnh di m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh l&ecirc;n  m Split View. Thanh iu khin t&aacute;c v v&agrave; status bar l&uacute;c n&agrave;y s c n  tn dng to&agrave;n b kh&ocirc;ng gian hin th ca m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. 5. C&aacute;c t&iacute;nh nng kh&aacute; th&uacute; v vi Camera ca m&aacute;y</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung cng &atilde; em n mt s chc nng kh&aacute; c &aacute;o cho ngi d&ugrave;ng khi s dng camera tr&ecirc;n in thoi &atilde; c l&ecirc;n h iu h&agrave;nh One UI 5.0. C th,  ch  chp  n c t&iacute;ch hp k&egrave;m vi phn c&agrave;i t camera th&igrave; bn c&oacute; th&ecirc;m kh nng zoom 3x. Bn cng c&oacute; th th&ecirc;m trc tip Watermark v&agrave;o nh sau khi chp.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, One UI 5 c&ograve;n em li kh nng nhn din vn bn qua h&igrave;nh nh, bn c&oacute; th chn v&agrave;o khu vc nh c&oacute; cha k&iacute; t  m&aacute;y t ng copy on vn bn &oacute; hoc t&igrave;m kim th&ocirc;ng tin tr&ecirc;n Google.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. 6. Trng th&aacute;i th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o (App Notifications) &amp; c&agrave;i t ng&ocirc;n ng ng dng (App Languages)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i t&ugrave;y chnh h thng giao din, Samsung c&ograve;n mang li cho ngi d&ugrave;ng nhng thit lp m&agrave; bn c&oacute; th thay i khi s dng ng dng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>u ti&ecirc;n, vi t&iacute;nh nng App Notifications th&igrave; bn c&oacute; th tin h&agrave;nh t&ugrave;y chnh c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh thc hin th th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o ca ng dng. C th, Samsung cho bn 3 t&ugrave;y chn mc nh bao gm hin th th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o theo dng banner  lockscreen, hin th s lng th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o mi ti icon ng dng v&agrave; hin th ca s pop-up th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o &oacute;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"thong-bao-samsung-one-ui-5-0\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/0WitYJeI-thong-bao-samsung-one-ui-5-0.jpg\" title=\"Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l 4\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, vi tng ng dng c c&agrave;i t trong m&aacute;y, bn cng c&oacute; th t&ugrave;y chnh ng&ocirc;n ng hin th ch&iacute;nh trong ng dng &oacute; nh ting Anh, ting Vit,&hellip;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. 7. Bo mt hn vi Security &amp; Privacy</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Vi h iu h&agrave;nh One IU 4.1 trc &acirc;y th&igrave; bn s nhn thy rt nhiu mc li&ecirc;n quan n bo mt ca m&aacute;y nh &ldquo;Biometrics and Security&rdquo; v&agrave; &ldquo;Privacy Dashboard&rdquo;. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n One Ui 5.0 th&igrave; tt c nhng t&iacute;nh nng bo mt thit b u &atilde; c Samsung gom v&agrave;o c&ugrave;ng mt mc c&oacute; t&ecirc;n Security &amp; Privacy  ngi d&ugrave;ng c&oacute; th theo d&otilde;i v&agrave; qun l&yacute; thit b trc quan hn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kh&ocirc;ng ch qun l&yacute; c quyn truy cp h thng ca c&aacute;c ng dng, cp ph&eacute;p quyn truy cp v&agrave;o camera, micro,.. ca tng ng dng m&agrave; vic qun l&yacute; file, folder tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y cng din ra d d&agrave;ng hn th&ocirc;ng qua Samsung Pass, Secure Folder, Biometrics, Private Share.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>2. C&oacute; n&ecirc;n cp nht One Ui 5.0 kh&ocirc;ng? Danh s&aacute;ch nhng thit b c cp nht phi&ecirc;n bn h iu h&agrave;nh One UI 5</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Giao din tng th ca h iu h&agrave;nh One UI 5 kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; nhiu thay i qu&aacute; ln so vi h iu h&agrave;nh One UI 4.1 trc &oacute; n&ecirc;n n&oacute; vn mang li mt s quen thuc cho ngi d&ugrave;ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, theo &aacute;nh gi&aacute; ca nhiu chuy&ecirc;n trang c&ocirc;ng ngh v&agrave; phn hi t&iacute;ch cc t ngi d&ugrave;ng th&igrave; h iu h&agrave;nh mi ca Samsung mang li tri nghim tng i mt m&agrave; v&agrave; nhiu t&iacute;nh nng &aacute;ng gi&aacute;.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"samsung-one-ui-5-0\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/H3nJ85Tf-samsung-one-ui-5-0.png\" title=\"Samsung One UI 5.0 c cp nht ti Vit Nam: Mt hn v nhiu tnh nng mi l 5\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, vi vic cp nht One UI 5&nbsp; th&igrave; v c bn bn cng s nhn c nhng ci tin t h iu h&agrave;nh mi Android 13 qua &oacute; gi&uacute;p ci thin hiu sut tr&ecirc;n in thoi ca bn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Danh s&aacute;ch c&aacute;c thit b c cp nht One UI 5:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Hin ti th&igrave; c&aacute;c phi&ecirc;n bn Samsung Galaxy S22 series &atilde; c cp nht phi&ecirc;n bn ch&iacute;nh thc ca One UI 5.0. Samsung cng &atilde; c&ocirc;ng b l tr&igrave;nh cp nht h iu h&agrave;nh n&agrave;y cho c&aacute;c thit b ca h v&agrave;o cui nm nay v&agrave; u nm 2023.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Theo &oacute;, c&aacute;c thit b Samsung Galaxy S20, Z Flip 3, Z Fold 3 tr v sau s c cp nht bn ch&iacute;nh thc One UI 5 v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 11.</p>'),
('97f21015-8c60-4548-8a0d-1119f48ef84f', 'en', 'Cch chi FIFA Online 4 ha cng khng kh World Cup', 'Cch chi FIFA Online 4 ha cng khng kh World Cup', 'FIFA Online 4 c xem nh l mt trong nhng con game bng  nh cao nht v ni ting trn ton th gii. Khng ch dng li l mt ta game gii tr, FIFA Online 4', '<h2>1. C&aacute;ch ti EA Sports FIFA Online 4</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>1.1 Th&ocirc;ng tin game FIFA Online 4</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>FIFA Online 4 l&agrave; ta game b&oacute;ng &aacute; do nh&agrave; ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh game EA Sport ph&aacute;t trin v&agrave; c qun l&yacute;  Vit Nam bi Garena Vit Nam.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ta game b&oacute;ng &aacute; n&agrave;y c &aacute;nh gi&aacute; cao bi h thng &acirc;m thanh v&agrave;  ha si&ecirc;u ch&acirc;n thc gi&uacute;p cho c&aacute;c game th tri nghim c kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; b&oacute;ng &aacute; s&aacute;t vi thc t nht. B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, tt c nhng chuyn ng ca cu th u rt mt m&agrave; v&agrave; uyn chuyn, t nhng thao t&aacute;c nh chuyn b&oacute;ng, &aacute;nh u, dt im u c i ng k s ca EA Sport m&ocirc; phng 3D ging nh tht.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>im ni bt nht v &acirc;m thanh ca ta game n&agrave;y &oacute; ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; bn c&oacute; th nghe c ting ca 2 B&igrave;nh lun vi&ecirc;n chuy&ecirc;n nghip Quang Huy v&agrave; Quang T&ugrave;ng trong mi trn u gi&uacute;p n&oacute; ging nh mt trn cu chuy&ecirc;n nghip hn bao gi ht.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"fifa-online-4\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://tech24h.hubs.vn/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2022/12/fifa-online-4.png\" title=\"Cch chi FIFA Online 4 ha cng khng kh World Cup 1\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>EA Sport c&oacute; mi quan h hp t&aacute;c v&agrave; bn quyn h&igrave;nh nh vi 32 gii u chuy&ecirc;n nghip kh&aacute;c nhau, qua &oacute; h&atilde;ng game n&agrave;y ng thi cng s hu h&igrave;nh nh ca hn 1500 cu th tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n th gii. Tp hp n&agrave;y bao gm c&aacute;c CLB v&agrave; cu th ca c&aacute;c gii v&ocirc; ch quc gia v&agrave; gii u cup ca c&aacute;c ch&acirc;u lc ln nh Ch&acirc;u &Acirc;u v&agrave; Ch&acirc;u &Aacute;,&hellip;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nu y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch i tuyn Vit Nam th&igrave; bn cng c&oacute; th t&igrave;m thy nhng danh th quen thuc nh Vn Hu, C&ocirc;ng Phng, Xu&acirc;n Trng, Vn Thanh,.. xut hin trong phi&ecirc;n bn FIFA Online 4 n&agrave;y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1.2 Li chi ca FIFA Online 4</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi chi FIFA Online 4, ngi chi s c&oacute; vai tr&ograve; nh mt nh&agrave; qun l&yacute; i b&oacute;ng chuy&ecirc;n nghip  thc hin c&aacute;c v chuyn nhng cu th, qun l&yacute; mc lng v&agrave; a ra nhng quyt nh v chin thut  c&oacute; th chin thng trn u.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>FIFA Online 4 c&oacute; h thng chi rt chuy&ecirc;n nghip gm nhiu ch  chi nh Xp hng n,&nbsp; xp hng 2vs2, giao hu, trn u gii v&agrave; Volta Live. Trong &oacute;, trn u gii l&agrave; c&aacute;c trn b&oacute;ng thuc h thng gii thi u gia ngi chi v&agrave; m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh  gi&uacute;p bn ci thin k nng ca bn th&acirc;n. Tuy vy, bn cng phi rt c gng v&agrave; c&oacute; li chi th&ocirc;ng minh  chin thng nhng trn u n&agrave;y v&agrave; ot c c&uacute;p.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, ngi chi cng c&oacute; th d d&agrave;ng thi u c&ugrave;ng vi nhng ngi chi kh&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n th gii hoc thc hin c&aacute;c trn b&oacute;ng c&ugrave;ng bn b&egrave; mt c&aacute;ch si&ecirc;u d d&agrave;ng nh h thng gh&eacute;p &ocirc;i d d&agrave;ng t game.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H thng rank tri d&agrave;i t nghip d 3 n si&ecirc;u sao  bn c&oacute; th c gng thi u n&acirc;ng cao xp hng ca m&igrave;nh.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>im thu h&uacute;t ca FIFA Online 4 chc chn l&agrave; ch  n&acirc;ng cp cu th v&agrave; m th y may ri. Ch&iacute;nh nh v&agrave;o iu n&agrave;y m&agrave; game ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng thu h&uacute;t c nhiu ngi chi hn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>2.3 Cu h&igrave;nh m&aacute;y gi &yacute;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>FIFA Online 4 l&agrave; mt ta game min ph&iacute; v&agrave; bn c&oacute; th ti xung v&agrave; c&agrave;i t game v thit b t trang 