ve;n ph&iacute;m&nbsp;<strong>FullSize</strong>, thun tin cho nhiu sinh vi&ecirc;n, nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n vn ph&ograve;ng khi phi hc tp v&agrave; l&agrave;m vic nhp liu nhiu con s. B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, khong c&aacute;ch gia c&aacute;c ph&iacute;m c thit k ho&agrave;n ho c&ugrave;ng vi  nhy tt em n cho bn cm gi&aacute;c g&otilde; ph&iacute;m thoi m&aacute;i, d chu v&agrave; &ecirc;m &aacute;i hn bao gi ht.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>S hu vi&ecirc;n pin thi lng ln, trang b cng kt ni a dng</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Vic trang b cho&nbsp;<strong>HP&nbsp;</strong>vi&ecirc;n pin lin&nbsp;<strong>3 cell&nbsp;</strong>c&oacute; c&ocirc;ng sut&nbsp;<strong>41Wh&nbsp;</strong>gi&uacute;p bn c&oacute; th tri nghim c&aacute;c t&aacute;c v c bn th&ocirc;ng thng c ng&agrave;y d&agrave;i m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng lo ngi vn  ht pin gia chng s dng, tin li cho vic bn phi mang laptop ca m&igrave;nh ra ngo&agrave;i  l&agrave;m vic v&agrave; hc tp.</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"Laptop HP 15s-fq5079TU 6K799PA | Dung lng pin\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/28/20220928_59da1693-2942-4e43-abb7-e5a52741514e.png\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra,<strong>&nbsp;HP 15s</strong>&nbsp;n&agrave;y c trang b nhiu cng kt ni nh:&nbsp;<strong>1 cng USB Type C</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>2 cng USB 3.1</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>1 cng SD card slot&nbsp;</strong>gi&uacute;p tng hiu sut truyn d liu. B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute; c&ograve;n c trang b&nbsp;<strong>1 c&ocirc;ng xu&acirc;t hinh HDMI&nbsp;</strong>gi&uacute;p truyn ti h&igrave;nh nh, video vi cht lng h&igrave;nh nh sc n&eacute;t.</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"Laptop HP 15s-fq5079TU 6K799PA | Cng kt ni\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/9/28/20220928_5729eabc-517e-4a66-99ab-ccb0bee4d4ad.png\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>Cui c&ugrave;ng,<strong>&nbsp;</strong>laptop HP 15s c h tr k&ecirc;t n&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng d&acirc;y<strong>&nbsp;WiFi 802.11ac v&agrave; Bluetooth</strong>&nbsp;c&oacute; kh nng truyn d liu vi c&aacute;c thit b kh&aacute;c mt c&aacute;ch nhanh ch&oacute;ng.</p>');
