('97efbf6d-e9cb-4788-a381-7dcd3885d5d0', 'en', 'Laptop ASUS Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W (i3-1115G4/RAM 4GB/512GB SSD/ Windows 11)', 'Laptop ASUS Vivobook', 'CPU: Intel Core i3-1115G4', '<h3><a href=\"https://phongvu.vn/c/laptop\"><strong>Laptop&nbsp;</strong></a><strong>Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W l&agrave; mt trong nhng d&ograve;ng laptop c nhiu sinh vi&ecirc;n a chung. Vi gi&aacute; th&agrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng qu&aacute; cao, chic laptop n&agrave;y nhanh ch&oacute;ng c sn &oacute;n vi thit k hin i v&agrave; hiu nng n nh, cho bn mt tri nghim th&uacute; v.&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Kiu d&aacute;ng thanh lch, nh gn d d&agrave;ng mang theo</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Laptop Asus Vivobook c&oacute; v ngo&agrave;i v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng bt mt vi kiu d&aacute;ng gn nh, thanh lch, m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh c&nbsp; thit k vin si&ecirc;u mng v&agrave; m&agrave;u x&aacute;m to&aacute;t l&ecirc;n v mnh m v&agrave; hin i. Phn vin m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh vn l&agrave; mt m&agrave;u en quen thuc v&agrave; logo ASUS to im nhn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | Thit k gn gng\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_051dfd2e-8a66-4630-9728-952529e41383.jpg\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>n tng hn na khi m&agrave; chic ASUS VivoBook X515EA n&agrave;y c&oacute; k&iacute;ch thc 36 x 23.5 x 1.99 cm c&ugrave;ng trng lng ch 1.8kg, rt nh d&ugrave; &acirc;y ch l&agrave; mt chic laptop 15,6 inch. Ph&iacute;a tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh cng c trang b mt chic VGA webcam tin li cho vic hc trc tuyn, hp online ca ngi d&ugrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>M&agrave;n h&igrave;nh 15,6 inch Full HD sc n&eacute;t, trang b tm nn IPS</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Laptop Asus X515EA-BQ2351W c trang b m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh 15.6 inch c&oacute;  ph&acirc;n gii l&agrave; 1920 x 1080 pixels (Full HD). Tm nn IPS ca chic m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh n&agrave;y cng cho kh nng hin th h&igrave;nh nh c sc n&eacute;t hn nhng m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh thng vi di m&agrave;u rng, gim c &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng xanh, tng cng c&aacute;c chi tit trong mi iu kin &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | Mn hnh 15.6 inch\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_86e4d140-54d8-4fd6-b5b9-02def6aee434.jpg\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>Th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o &oacute;, em laptop n&agrave;y cng s hu m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh chng l&oacute;a gi&uacute;p m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng b ch&oacute;i s&aacute;ng, b b&oacute;ng gng k c trong c&aacute;c iu kin &aacute;nh s&aacute;ng gt. C&ugrave;ng vi &oacute;, m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh n&agrave;y cng gi&uacute;p ngi d&ugrave;ng tr&aacute;nh mi mt khi s dng trong mt thi gian d&agrave;i, ph&ugrave; hp vi d&acirc;n vn ph&ograve;ng hay sinh vi&ecirc;n phi d&ugrave;ng m&aacute;y thng xuy&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Hiu nng n nh, Intel Core i3-1115G4&nbsp; cho mi t&aacute;c v mt m&agrave;</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W c&oacute; mt cu h&igrave;nh l&yacute; tng cho c&ocirc;ng vic vn ph&ograve;ng khi sc mnh ca m&aacute;y kh&ocirc;ng ch n t b vi x l&yacute; Intel core i3-1115G4 ( 3.0 GHz - 4.10 GHz / 6MB / 2 nh&acirc;n, 4 lu&ocirc;ng) m&agrave; c&ograve;n t b nh RAM 1 x 4GB Onboard DDR4 (1 khe cm) cho hiu nng s dng cao.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | Hiu nng mnh m\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_51218c7d-8fcf-4db8-91ce-e2ea2d0ac8ae.jpg\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>Con chip n&agrave;y tit kim pin khi c sn xut tr&ecirc;n tin tr&igrave;nh 10nm SuperFin ti&ecirc;n tin. Trong khi &oacute; RAM 4GB DDR4 on board cng gi&uacute;p ngi d&ugrave;ng vn h&agrave;nh m&aacute;y c mt m&agrave; v&agrave; trn tru hn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Trang b chip &ocirc; hoa Intel UHD Graphics v&agrave;&nbsp;  cng 512GB SSD</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, Vivobook X515EA s hu chip &ocirc; hoa Intel UHD Graphics cng gi&uacute;p bn c&oacute; th thc hin c&aacute;c t&aacute;c v vn ph&ograve;ng c bn, hay duyt web, gii tr&iacute;, xem phim, office c bn mt c&aacute;ch mt m&agrave; hn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | Dung lng lu tr cao\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_7289ad5f-a4ac-4e24-8cb7-a2b2a504e9e1.jpg\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>Th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o &oacute;, laptop Asus Vivobook n&agrave;y c&ograve;n c&oacute; sn  cng 512GB SSD M.2 NVMe, va cho dung lng lu tr ln, va c&oacute; th&nbsp; tng tc to&agrave;n din m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh.  cng n&agrave;y kt hp vi b nh RAM ca m&aacute;y, cho bn mt kh&ocirc;ng gian va  cho vic lu tr t&agrave;i liu, h&igrave;nh nh, video d d&agrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>H tr y  kt ni, h iu h&agrave;nh Windows 11 Home</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Chic laptop Asus cng h tr y  nhng kt ni ph bin nh: 1 cng USB 3.2 Type C, 1 cng USB 3.2 , 2 cng USB 2.0, 1 cng HDMI. Nh y  cng kt ni tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh n&agrave;y c&oacute; th kt ni vi mi thit b ngoi vi  phc v ti u cho c&ocirc;ng vic ca bn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"Laptop Asus Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W | a dng cng kt ni\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/teko-gae.appspot.com/media/image/2022/3/14/20220314_6839c0d9-2a49-4df6-8809-2008858215ac.jpg\" /></figure>\r\n\r\n<p>ASUS &atilde; trang b cho chic laptop Vivobook X515EA-BQ2351W h iu h&agrave;nh Windows 11 Home, cho ph&eacute;p bn c tri nghim phi&ecirc;n bn Windows bn quyn trn vn m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng lo mt ph&iacute;. Win 11 vi nhng ci tin v giao din v&agrave; c n&acirc;ng cao bo mt,&nbsp; gi&uacute;p ti u c hiu sut c&ocirc;ng vic ca ngi d&ugrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><strong>Trang b cm bin v&acirc;n tay, Pin 2 cell 37Wh</strong></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Laptop Asus X515EA-BQ2351W c trang b cm bin v&acirc;n tay t&iacute;ch hp ngay trong touchpad ca m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh cho ph&eacute;p ngi d&ugrave;ng ch mt &uacute;ng mt c&uacute